<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%- include('../partials/head.ejs') %>

<body>

    <%- include('../partials/header.ejs') %>


    <main>

        <div class="arrow-header-price-img"><img src="/img/articles/arrow-div.png" alt=""></div>

    <form action="/" method=""  class="form-max-final-step-container">

        <article>
            <section class="form-create-5">
                <div class="text-header-create-container">
                    <span class="title-step-5">Completa la información de tu producto</span>
                    <span class="step-5">Paso 5 de 6</span>
                    <p class="paragraph-step-5">Para no perder exposición, asegúrate de que la primera foto tenga fondo
                        blanco puro creado
                        con un editor de fotos.</p>
                </div>
    
                <div class="form-dropArea-imgs">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-camera"></i>
                    <label for="foto" class="custom-file-input">
                        <input type="file" id="foto" name="foto" accept="image/*" required>
                    </label>
                </div>
            </section>
    
            <hr>

            <section class="form-create-6">
                <div class="text-header-create-container">
                    <span class="title-step-6">Para terminar, definamos las condiciones de venta</span>
                    <span class="step-6">Paso 6 de 6</span>
                </div>
    
                <div class="form-image-price">
    
                    <div class="input-information-container">
                        <label for="precio" class="priceText">¿Cuál es el precio?</label>
                        <input type="number" id="precio" name="precio" min="0" step="0.01" required placeholder="$">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </article>
                 

        <div class="buttons-submit-step-5-6">
            <input type="submit" value="Confirmar" class="input-continue-step-5-6">
            <input type="submit" value="Cancelar" class="input-cancell-step-5-6">
        </div>
    </form>

    </main>

</body>

</html>